0.title: Welcome to Rocket

1.title: Welcome to Rocket
1.headline: Small
1.body: No overblown tools or frontend frameworks, add JavaScript and/or Web Components only on pages where needed.

2.title: Welcome to Rocket
2.headline: 0 JavaScript by default
2.body: Server side rendered Web Components means NO JavaScript by default.

3.title: Welcome to Rocket
3.headline: Zero Configuration
3.body: Automatic code splitting, filesystem based routing, and JavaScript in Markdown.

4.title: Welcome to Rocket
4.headline: Meta Framework
4.body:
Build on top of giants like Modern Web ,
      Lit , and
      Rollup 
      .

5.title: Welcome to Rocket
5.headline: Theme Support
5.body: You have the content - we have the themes - or you build your own

6.title: Welcome to Rocket
6.headline: Always fast while developing
6.body: While developing only pages you visit get rendered - so even with 1000 pages it will start up fast. Additionally assets are not moved but only referenced.

7.title: Welcome to Rocket
7.headline: Fast for users
7.body: An optimized rollup configuration means that the page will load faster for users, even if you have a slow connection.

8.title: Welcome to Rocket
8.headline: Batteries included
8.body: Comes with page navigation, 404 page, social media sharing, ...

9.title: Welcome to Rocket
9.headline: Do less work
9.body: Rocket does exactly the amount of work it needs to show you the content you want. No more waiting for the server to render pages or copy assets.
